Name: Ultra hype song
Description: This song makes you want to set a new PR in the gym, buy another round of shots, or chug coffee and finish your excel spreadsheet for work before midnight.

Name: Song by an artist with <100k monthly Spotify listeners
Description:
You're probably the only person in this league who's heard this song by a less-than-famous artist. As long as they have less than 100k monthly listeners, any song is fair game. 

*Note: This was previously <500k, but I changed it to make it harder.*

Name: Song most likely to be banned by republicans
Description: You need to find a song that Karoline Leavitt, MTG, and Marco Rubio do NOT want children to listen to

Name: Song with a rap feature in an otherwise non-rap song
Description: This is a surprise rap verse, a pleasant surprise, popping up in a song that doesn't otherwise have rap vibes.

Name: Song less than 2 minutes in length
Description: This song is short and sweet. Must be LESS THAN 2 minutes long, not equal to or longer than 2 minutes.

Name: Song that's not in English
Description: No English allowed in this round. That's the only rule.

Name: One-man band

Name: Best song by an artist who's under 18 years old (when released)
Description: Age is just a number. As long as they're under 18 years old when the song comes out, anything goes.
